other:
	datePosted
	date
	The date this job was posted, given as RFC 3339 date-time format.

	code
	string
	The job's code. Codes are expected to be unique within open jobs.

	title
	string
	The job's title.

	description
	string
	The job's description, as suitable for external job seekers.
	internalDescription	string	The job's description, as suitable for internal job seekers. Only use this if you have a way of identifying the audience as being internal.

	categoryValues
	array
	An array of ids for category values that are attached to this job. Only category values for category types that are "appliesToJobs" or "appliesToJobSeekers" will be returned.

	canonicalURL
	an encoded URL
	The URL of this job at its "source", i.e. within SnapHire.

	availableToPublicJobSeekers
	boolean
	Whether public job seekers can apply for this job (assuming the job is open).

	availableToInternalJobSeekers
	boolean
	Whether internal job seekers can apply for this job (assuming the job is open).
